==Google and censorship issues==
  +   +
Google, along with Yahoo! and MSN participates in [[China]]'s [[internet censorship]] program, commonly referred to as the [[Great Firewall of China]]. The Chinese version of Google, www.google.cn, limits search results on such topics as the [[Tianmen Square Massacre]], and other topics considered off-limits by Chinese authorities.
